her loses his job.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":0.9928,"vote_count":267,"poster_path":"/6Y0ZRyh5eH7WLY4fcF92swhtgUz.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-27","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/1aAR1XHBYaqnKzRUH3bL7KpXMhs.jpg","original_title":"トウキョウソナタ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":8938,"adult":false,"title":"Tokyo!","video":false,"overview":"Three distinct tales unfold in the bustling city of Tokyo. Merde, a bizarre sewer-dweller, emerges from a manhole and begins terrorizing pedestrians. After his arrest, he stands trial and lashes out at a hostile courtroom. A man who has resigned himself to a life of solitude reconsiders after meeting a charming pizza delivery woman. And finally, a happy young couple find themselves undergoing a series of frightening metamorphoses.","genre_ids":[35,18,14,10749],"popularity":4.2372,"vote_count":257,"poster_path":"/6xbq2EBAOwy0V7bzd1um3sJX1jd.jpg","release_date":"2008-08-16","vote_average":6.891,"backdrop_path":"/hUpP1NUVKCg66xFBWjSSxaLzJx9.jpg","original_title":"TOKYO!","original_language":"ja"},{"id":9346,"adult":false,"title":"Risky Business","video":false,"overview":"Meet Joel Goodson, an industrious, college-bound 17-year-old and a responsible, trustworthy son. However, when his parents go away and leave him home alone in the wealthy Chicago suburbs with the Porsche at his disposal he quickly decides he has been good for too long and it is time to enjoy himself. After an unfortunate incident with the Porsche Joel must raise some cash, in a risky way.","genre_ids":[10749,35,18],"popularity":2.9652,"vote_count":1420,"poster_path":"/82KOHShH9raGhkcAN3TztVjqjj3.jpg","release_date":"1983-08-05","vote_average":6.592,"backdrop_path":"/xGEBZAFcRQ8fqGVXMtQCnkoUNTG.jpg","original_title":"Risky Business","original_language":"en"},{"id":9437,"adult":false,"title":"Kiss the Girls","video":false,"overview":"Forensic psychologist and detective Alex Cross travels to North Carolina and teams with escaped kidnap victim Kate McTiernan to hunt down \"Casanova,\" a serial killer who abducts strong-willed women and forces them to submit to his demands. The trail leads to Los Angeles, where the duo discovers that the psychopath may not be working alone.","genre_ids":[53,80,9648,18],"popularity":3.8215,"vote_count":1833,"poster_path":"/25h5I3E3ydhazsPDnscWHivq5pn.jpg","release_date":"1997-09-29","vote_average":6.528,"backdrop_path":"/y319VH0gIFie6KEO5L4nHhxxQUw.jpg","original_title":"Kiss the Girls","original_language":"en"},{"id":9464,"adult":false,"title":"Buffalo '66","video":false,"overview":"Billy is released after five years in prison. In the next moment, he kidnaps teenage student Layla and visits his parents with her, pretending she is his girlfriend and they will soon marry.","genre_ids":[18,10749,35],"popularity":2.6642,"vote_count":1023,"poster_path":"/fxzXFzbSGNA52NHQCMqQiwzMIQw.jpg","release_date":"1998-01-20","vote_average":7.142,"backdrop_path":"/oCcRRoalUWy83x3gqhCIl6pPUAi.jpg","original_title":"Buffalo '66","original_language":"en"},{"id":9539,"adult":false,"title":"Martyrs","video":false,"overview":"A young woman’s quest for revenge against the people who kidnapped and tortured her as a child leads her and her best friend, also a victim of child abuse, on a terrifying journey into a living hell of depravity.","genre_ids":[27,18,53],"popularity":4.8992,"vote_count":2956,"poster_path":"/2zj5JHihR3Bih8vZROJK9LOWsZO.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-12","vote_average":7.304,"backdrop_path":"/fO1hwjlUqDe1ixO7eMfxTby62Ut.jpg","original_title":"Martyrs","original_language":"fr"},{"id":9571,"adult":false,"title":"Dazed and Confused","video":false,"overview":"The adventures of a group of Texas teens on their last day of school in 1976, centering on student Randall Floyd, who moves easily among stoners, jocks and geeks. Floyd is a star athlete, but he also likes smoking weed, which presents a conundrum when his football coach demands he sign a \"no drugs\" pledge.","genre_ids":[35,18],"popularity":3.5553,"vot